`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Continual_Light
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'continual light'
 * cast 'continual light' <object>

 This spell creates a ball of light, which you can hold as a light source. The
ball of light will last indefinitely. It may also be used on an object to give
it an enchanted glow.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
